  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/264956ee68547b1f482f8203445a0b05.avif?t=1770240995\" width=686 height=4300 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/c2cd76453d16adf69d1ae0a1db19979a.avif?t=1770240995\" width=584 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a Picnic solo or with up to three friends in online co-op! Strategize builds, complete objectives, and defeat monster hordes to prepare for massive boss battles! In the Zone, Loners that stick together survive. Sometimes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/47450813ffb8c15141344383e2c3cf1e.poster.avif?t=1770240995\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/47450813ffb8c15141344383e2c3cf1e.webm?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/47450813ffb8c15141344383e2c3cf1e.mp4?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/bbd79fed78f609ff5121289c16fde2f9.avif?t=1770240995\" width=584 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your IMPULSE GEAR transforms every arena into a high-flying playground of destruction! Turn every ramp into a launchpad, every cliff into an advantage, and every mini-boss into easy pickings from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/39601ffcc27384f74d5816b14b7e9bbc.poster.avif?t=1770240995\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/39601ffcc27384f74d5816b14b7e9bbc.webm?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/39601ffcc27384f74d5816b14b7e9bbc.mp4?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/2fd565b6c552d0473571869b8193c48f.avif?t=1770240995\" width=590 height=129 /></span>Shoot spirals of shurikens or blaze fiery Rocket  trails. Every upgrade combo creates harmonic chaos. Stack Cursed Curios, trigger evolutions, and rain explosive meteor storms on your enemies for devastating effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/52e38a7c9582812493b03500fa2201e7.poster.avif?t=1770240995\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/52e38a7c9582812493b03500fa2201e7.webm?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/52e38a7c9582812493b03500fa2201e7.mp4?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/b9da4bdfc56e749d6af7374929600888.avif?t=1770240995\" width=585 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is still being developed, but we want to encourage everyone to participate! We have an active Discord server and would love to hear your feedback and questions!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/c2cd76453d16adf69d1ae0a1db19979a.avif?t=1770240995\" width=584 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a Picnic solo or with up to three friends in online co-op! Strategize builds, complete objectives, and defeat monster hordes to prepare for massive boss battles! In the Zone, Loners that stick together survive. Sometimes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/47450813ffb8c15141344383e2c3cf1e.poster.avif?t=1770240995\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/47450813ffb8c15141344383e2c3cf1e.webm?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/47450813ffb8c15141344383e2c3cf1e.mp4?t=1770240995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/bbd79fed78f609ff5121289c16fde2f9.avif?t=1770240995\" width=584 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your IMPULSE GEAR transforms every arena into a high-flying playground of destruction! Turn every ramp into a launchpad, every cliff into an advantage, and every mini-boss into easy pickings from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903560/extras/39601ffcc2